{"tid":1956623,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"李嘉誠及李澤鉅成功撈貨，2個星期已經賺左接近一億！！！","createTime":"2020-04-03T10:02:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T05:45:20.000Z","uid":118346,"like":457,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":103,"replies":[{"pid":"d0bd510a6838d6f2860239425a96a8a694c1a317","tid":1956623,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T10:02:54.000Z","msg":"股市連日下挫，連港人最愛的匯豐(<a href=\"http://005.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F005.HK&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2BhV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=53d0fbbb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">005.HK</a>)亦跌穿40元，恒生指數力守23,000點。別人恐慌時我貪婪，李嘉誠父子最近頻頻出手增持旗下長實集團(<a href=\"http://1113.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F1113.HK&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2BhV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=3e86713e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">1113.HK</a>)股權。<br />\n<br />\n李嘉誠及李澤鉅透過兩人各自擁有50%權益之公司在上月20日、23日、24日、25日、26日及30日，6日間合共以約6億9,424萬港元增持了約1,842萬股長實集團。<br />\n<br />\n以今日長實股價$42.8元計算，李嘉誠及李澤鉅帳面已經賺取了約9,730萬元。若自李氏父子開始出手該日開始計算，13日間平均每日賺近750萬。"},{"pid":"fe715ff416cb05ce410ef4996c79addb2af26c99","tid":1956623,"uid":118346,"like":85,"dislike":1,"score":84,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T10:04:14.000Z","msg":"原來今日收市已經係 43.55 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"311f67b37aebafb758418bdf8af6ba48a67bb464","tid":1956623,"uid":133528,"like":316,"dislike":28,"score":288,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T10:04:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cgp7Noq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgp7Noq.png&h=203385e9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"952d6fd9cede30ad2f8d3773e05f58953e892ae0","tid":1956623,"uid":122377,"like":100,"dislike":0,"score":100,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T10:06:16.000Z","msg":"佢2父子好少益股東 有緣咪跟下"},{"pid":"278c0d834c273d7cca16253a3148912a36ce56ba","tid":1956623,"uid":72629,"like":221,"dislike":0,"score":221,"citedBy":2,"replyT